<div class='carouselRow' style='width: 3600px'>
<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_44654627'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44654627-one-of-us-is-next"><img alt="One of Us Is Next (One of Us Is Lying, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1558455815l/44654627._SX98_.jpg" />
